{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.000", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.840", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.320", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kollegen und Kolleginnen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.280", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Zuh\u00f6rerinnen und Zuh\u00f6rer auf den Trib\u00fcnen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.080", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt viele Emotionen bei diesem Thema. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.600", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte noch einmal klarstellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.680", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber was wir sprechen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.800", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht um die Rekrutierung Minderj\u00e4hriger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.320", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht um Kindersoldaten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.960", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist uns klar."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.600", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Danke; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.560", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gerne klatschen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.240", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht schlicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.920", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir f\u00fcr die Einhaltung des Ziels Straight\u00a018 pl\u00e4dieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.560", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das bedeutet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.720", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass keine Minderj\u00e4hrigen in der Bundeswehr verpflichtet werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.320", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "klar und ohne Ausnahmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.400", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.360", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Milit\u00e4rdienst erst ab 18\u00a0Jahren aufgenommen werden kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.200", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Punkt! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.200", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit wenden wir uns nicht gegen die Bundeswehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.040", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern setzen uns f\u00fcr Minderj\u00e4hrige ein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.880", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Davon spricht unser Antrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.240", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und davon spricht der Antrag der Linken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.920", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist uns nat\u00fcrlich v\u00f6llig klar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.960", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir nicht \u00fcber Kindersoldaten im klassischen Sinn sprechen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.800", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die aufgrund ihrer Armut zum Milit\u00e4r gehen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.240", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in Kriegen eingesetzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.800", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind in Deutschland gl\u00fccklicherweise in der Lage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.680", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Kinder in diesem Alter in die Schule gehen und in Frieden leben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.240", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Trotzdem sprechen wir heute \u00fcber Jugendliche, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.680", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die unter 18\u00a0Jahre alt sind und sich bei der Bundeswehr verpflichten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.960", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sehen das kritisch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.280", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundeswehr ist eben kein Arbeitgeber wie alle anderen auch; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.240", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn junge Menschen werden dort zum Dienst an der Waffe ausgebildet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.920", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das macht einen Unterschied."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.960", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade wenn es um so wichtige und weitreichende Entscheidungen wie die Verpflichtung bei der Bundeswehr geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.720", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind sich Jugendliche \u00fcber die Konsequenzen oft nicht bewusst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.840", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das zeigt auch die hohe Abbrecherquote. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.320", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Circa ein Viertel der Freiwilligen quittiert vorzeitig den Dienst."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.200", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fakt ist aber nat\u00fcrlich auch\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.880", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wei\u00df ich\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.440", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundeswehr hat seit der Aussetzung der Wehrpflicht ein Nachwuchsproblem und steht in Konkurrenz mit Ausbildungsbetrieben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.760", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fachhochschulen und Universit\u00e4ten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.280", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben nun aber die Situation\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.920", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das haben wir heute oft geh\u00f6rt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.440", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die Zahl der Minderj\u00e4hrigen bei der Bundeswehr seit 2011 mehr als verdreifacht hat; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.560", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das zeigt auch der aktuelle Bericht des Wehrbeauftragten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.120", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist in unseren Augen keine gute Entwicklung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.040", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben in den letzten Jahren viel dar\u00fcber geh\u00f6rt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.520", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Norbert M\u00fcller hat das auch gesagt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.600", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass auf allen m\u00f6glichen Kan\u00e4len sehr viel f\u00fcr die Bundeswehr geworben wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.360", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass unter 18-J\u00e4hrige angeworben wurden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.760", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es Abenteuercamps gab, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.440", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Lust auf eine Ausbildung machen und diese in sch\u00f6nen Farben schildern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.040", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gab auch gezielte Werbung in Schulen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.480", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo Videos gezeigt wurden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.800", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die Ausbildung als sch\u00f6n darstellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.400", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist aber wenig \u00fcber die Aufgabe und die Pflichten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.560", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ein Soldat oder eine Soldatin dann wirklich hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.040", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gesagt worden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.720", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage das als Tochter eines Soldaten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.600", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich bin als Soldatenkind aufgewachsen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.560", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist ja mehr als das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.200", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was in der Werbung sch\u00f6n aussieht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.880", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine milit\u00e4rische Ausbildung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.440", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.440", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist eben kein Dschungelcamp, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.480", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kein Computerspiel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.560", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern eine ernste Angelegenheit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.400", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Berichte \u00fcber die H\u00e4ufung von sexueller Bel\u00e4stigung und rechtsextremen Str\u00f6mungen sowie gewaltvollen Initiationsriten deuten doch\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.720", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sage ich als Mutter von f\u00fcnf Kindern\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.440", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht auf ein passendes Umfeld f\u00fcr Minderj\u00e4hrige hin."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.480", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So klar ich sehe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.120", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die Bundeswehr um Nachwuchs bem\u00fchen muss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.840", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und so wenig ich eine schlechte Absicht unterstelle\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.320", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch wir als gr\u00fcne Fraktion haben ein Interesse daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.280", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere Parlamentsarmee zu unterst\u00fctzen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.200", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so sehr appelliere ich immer und immer wieder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.640", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "junge Menschen bei der Bundeswehr erst unter Vertrag zu nehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.520", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie 18\u00a0Jahre alt sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.960", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich pl\u00e4diere f\u00fcr eine klare Haltung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.680", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann ist die Bundesregierung im Kampf gegen Kindersoldaten glaubhaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.360", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie selbst konsequent handelt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.840", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn das in anderen L\u00e4ndern wie zum Beispiel in Irland geht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.920", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das haben wir geh\u00f6rt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.920", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann m\u00fcssen wir nicht hinterherhinken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.960", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns klare Kante zeigen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.600", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kein Kind, "
   ]
